{"type":"message","id":"63c658c2","parentId":"6b81ab2d","timestamp":"2026-04-03T12:07:29.074Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec_1775218048896_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Approval required (id be89c638, full be89c638-f87f-44d5-8967-c290913ab8b3).\nHost: gateway\nCWD: /home/node/.openclaw/workspace\nCommand:\n```sh\nls -F /home/node/.openclaw/workspace/skills/\n```\nMode: foreground (interactive approvals available).\nBackground mode requires pre-approved policy (allow-always or ask=off).\nReply with: /approve be89c638 allow-once|allow-always|deny\nIf the short code is ambiguous, use the full id in /approve."}],"details":{"status":"approval-pending","approvalId":"be89c638-f87f-44d5-8967-c290913ab8b3","approvalSlug":"be89c638","expiresAtMs":1775219849060,"allowedDecisions":["allow-once","allow-always","deny"],"host":"gateway","command":"ls -F /home/node/.openclaw/workspace/skills/","cwd":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace","warningText":""},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775218049067}}
{"type":"message","id":"54e61fb2","parentId":"63c658c2","timestamp":"2026-04-03T12:07:30.905Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<final>You are absolutely right to point that out! My apologies. The list I provided earlier (`clawflow`, `healthcheck`, `weather`, etc.) are what OpenClaw considers \"system-level\" skills, which are globally available.\n\nIt appears you have a separate set of skills located directly within your workspace at `/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/skills/`. I need your approval to list them to confirm.\n\nPlease `/approve` the command to list the contents of your workspace skills directory:</final>"}],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","usage":{"input":22162,"output":109,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22271,"cost":{"input":0.006648599999999999,"output":0.0002725,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0069210999999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775218049076,"responseId":"gq3PaezIB_OhkdUP54DOqQo"}}
